  "1893440": {
    "name": "直入炼狱",
    "steam_appid": 1893440,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/6828fef27af90e663c8e323af186f399.poster.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/6828fef27af90e663c8e323af186f399.webm?t=1763465318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/6828fef27af90e663c8e323af186f399.mp4?t=1763465318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >整装待发，直入炼狱！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >T̴̨̈́h̴̛͉e̷̦͌ ̷̡́I̷̫̐ń̵̦v̸̢̈́e̷͇͐r̷̩͋ẗ̷͈́ḛ̸̽d̵̬̆ ̵̀ͅT̶̖̈́o̵͎͋w̶̹̾e̸͎͊r̷̬͝的仆从们每晚都会出没，将那些胆小懦弱的人从家中拖入塔的深渊，一去不复返。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由你来勇敢面对地下的危险。由你来击杀恐怖的幕后黑手。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不断深入……直入炼狱。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/baff2c42e761ca81b64a98d7381fe68a.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=300 /></span>《直入炼狱》中的每一件物品都是独一无二的，能够真正改变你的游戏方式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的招式：</strong> 剑可格挡，斧能劈砍，灯笼即使收起后仍会发光——每件物品都有两种招式（并且通常隐藏着秘密！）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>附魔与诅咒：</strong> 寻找那些被黑暗魔法赋予了特殊属性的物品！它们的属性会发生彻底改变！注入法术、元素亲和力、突变等——期待意外惊喜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>能力而非属性：</strong> 这里没有“+2%火焰抗性”——武器和护甲能够解锁新的能力和力量来面对敌人，而不是小幅增加属性。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/2d117a6c830c803f13bab69c0bae2893.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=300 /></span>等待你的冒险既致命又不可预测——无论你面对多少次。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>意外的危险：</strong> T̴̨̈́h̴̛͉e̷̦͌ ̷̡́I̷̫̐ń̵̦v̸̢̈́e̷͇͐r̷̩͋ẗ̷͈́ḛ̸̽d̵̬̆ ̵̀ͅT̶̖̈́o̵͎͋w̶̹̾e̸͎͊r̷̬͝迷宫般的地牢充满诅咒，每一次尝试都会改变其布局。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>有意义的选择：</strong> 物品不仅强大，还非常稀缺，你只能带走你能携带的东西。每次死亡时，敌人、陷阱和危险都会发生变化——但你的选择也会影响每次结果。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>死亡，重生，再战：</strong>《直入炼狱》非常困难——每个敌人都是重大威胁，不能掉以轻心。你需要学会适应面对的危险，否则你将惨遭灭顶之灾。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/3618a5e2b2242940c0666a3c123df2d2.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=300 /></span>深入一个疯狂的世界——恶魔与死亡、折磨与疯狂在等着你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>面对地狱群魔：</strong> 恶魔们侵扰着《直入炼狱》的地牢，施展可怕的超自然力量。为了生存，你需要用尽一切技巧和勇气。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>英雄变成背叛者：</strong> T̴̨̈́h̴̛͉e̷̦͌ ̷̡́I̷̫̐ń̵̦v̸̢̈́e̷͇͐r̷̩͋ẗ̷͈́ḛ̸̽d̵̬̆ ̵̀ͅT̶̖̈́o̵͎͋w̶̹̾e̸͎͊r̷̬͝已被昔日的英雄接管，他们现在站在邪恶一边。是什么导致了这一转变？是什么黑暗目的驱使他们？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>黑暗秘密等待揭示：</strong> 探索tḧ̶͉́e̴̢͂ t̶̼̂e̴̙͑r̶͕͘r̶͚͉̈́ḯ̷͕b̶̻͖͛l̸̜̈e̷̜͗ ̵̛͓̒ t̵̰̜͝ṟ̶̪̈́̚u̸̪͔̾͘t̶̟̀͜h̶̺̓̈,̵͎̍̓ ̸̧̍t̴̢̛̤͛h̴͉͎̅a̴͍̖͗̍t̸̨̺͐̅█̸̢̀͝█̵̼́ ̸̛̬̗͝█̸̻̩͘ ̶̡̙̅█̷̣͎̅█̶̹͒█̸̪̾͂ ̶̨̯̓█̵͚͐̚█̴̭̞̏͠ ̴̦̅█̴̢̘͒█̸̭̅█̷̥̀█̵̢͝█̵̲̗̔͊█̴̞̳͑͛█̷̫͍͂█̶̬͔͒█̴̡̤̒́█̶̛̬ͅ █̷͓̎͗͜█̴͔͚́̀█̵̬̹̍̈́█̸̜̔█̸͍̐ █̸̦͎̈█̵̗̓͘█̴͚̌͜█̶̬̪̑̀█̷͓̳͂█̴̗̮͑ █̴̢͔̿͠█̸̞̙̊█̶̹̻̂█̶͙̔̀█̵̟̹̂̐█̷̰̳̈́̎█̵̧̱͒█̷̖̗̐̂█̷̜̯̓̑ █̶̢̩͐̔█̶̬̍̆█̷͎̤̅͌█̷͔͠ █̴̨̺̑́█̴̯̀̉ͅ█̵͙͖̀̿█̵͓̰͌█̵̝͉̏█̶̭̅̐█̴̬̱̂</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/cb16e5f68538ee378cb0b80fea53486d.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=300 /></span>&quot;…你不信？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你觉得这个致命的地牢不过是小菜一碟？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >很好。来玩玩试玩版，亲自体验一番吧。但请注意！那些踏入邪恶深渊的人，鲜有安然返回的…&quot;</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/9a01d20ba8eeead7b56751c95007a5d5.poster.avif?t=1763465318\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/9a01d20ba8eeead7b56751c95007a5d5.webm?t=1763465318\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1893440/extras/9a01d20ba8eeead7b56751c95007a5d5.mp4?t=1763465318\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
